  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0dbb \u0d85\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dd9\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d87\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd6\u0da9\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc5\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dad\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "They come to get oil from a fake number and reach the cage",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Wayangoda Police say that a motorcyclist and a bus driver who came to get fuel from Sipetco filling station in Medagampitiya, Weyangoda with fake number plates were arrested along with the respective vehicles.",
        "Two residents of Divulapitiya and Hindenia-Pattigoda areas have been arrested.",
        "As fuel is dispensed according to the last number of the number plate, it was revealed that the number plates were changed to match the last numbers of the day and when the police officers checked the respective motorcycle and bus that came to the fuel station, it was revealed that fake number plates were installed.",
        "The motorcycle and the bus were seized on the instructions of Chief Inspector Channa Vathewa, Police Station Officer, Veyangoda."
      ],
